{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","title":"BMAD Getting Started sebagai literature note","desc":"Catatan literature halaman BMAD Getting Started: orientasi workflow AI-native, bukan sekadar instalasi.","tags":["bmad","getting-started","literature"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"53f1c6cf97426a43b7b3b1084c672440","updated":1776914282340,"created":1776914282340,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","id":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.bmad","alias":"bmad","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.bmad"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","id":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.getting-started","alias":"getting-started","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.getting-started"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","id":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.literature","alias":"literature","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.literature"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","id":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260421170812","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":3,"offset":1125},"end":{"line":30,"column":28,"offset":1150},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260421170812"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","id":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260421172800","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":3,"offset":1250},"end":{"line":31,"column":28,"offset":1275},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260421172800"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":130,"column":3,"offset":12043},"end":{"line":130,"column":45,"offset":12085},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.ai-native","id":"zettel.moc.ai-native","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":246},"end":{"line":9,"column":45,"offset":288},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.literature.bmad-getting-started"}],"anchors":{"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan yang dibuka","value":"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"ringkasan-literatur":{"type":"header","text":"Ringkasan literatur","value":"ringkasan-literatur","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2},"ide-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Ide penting","value":"ide-penting","line":26,"column":0,"depth":2},"interpretasi":{"type":"header","text":"Interpretasi","value":"interpretasi","line":32,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":36,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":40,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"ae3bw38eg7l5p3ntry27x87","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bmad-getting-started-sebagai-literature-note\">BMAD Getting Started sebagai literature note<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bmad-getting-started-sebagai-literature-note\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Apa pesan utama dari halaman BMAD Getting Started?</li>\n<li>Mengapa onboarding BMAD lebih tentang workflow daripada installasi?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana Getting Started menghubungkan analyses, agents, dan project context?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"ringkasan-literatur\">Ringkasan literatur<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ringkasan-literatur\"></a></h2>\n<p>Halaman BMAD Getting Started memperkenalkan BMAD sebagai framework workflow AI-native engineering, bukan sekadar tool setup. Fokusnya pada alur kerja: aktivasi project context, penentuan agent, dan penggunaan phase yang terstruktur.</p>\n<p>Getting Started menekankan bahwa sukses BMAD datang dari cara tim memetakan peran, konteks, dan metode kerja, bukan hanya dari instalasi packages.</p>\n<h2 id=\"ide-penting\">Ide penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ide-penting\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>onboarding BMAD harus membangun mental model workflow, bukan hanya jalanin CLI.</li>\n<li>project context adalah input bersama yang mengikat semua agent.</li>\n<li>fase dan agent perlu dipahami sebagai bagian dari satu sistem terintegrasi.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"interpretasi\">Interpretasi<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#interpretasi\"></a></h2>\n<p>Catatan ini merekam bahwa BMAD onboarding adalah pengenalan psikologis terhadap cara kerja AI-native, bukan dokumentasi teknis semata.</p>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.bmad-method.org/tutorials/getting-started/\">https://docs.bmad-method.org/tutorials/getting-started/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421170812\">BMAD Getting Started mengajarkan workflow awal AI-native engineering, bukan sekadar installasi</a> — BMAD Getting Started mengajarkan workflow awal AI-native engineering, bukan sekadar installasi</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421172800\">BMAD project context adalah konstitusi implementasi untuk AI agents, bukan dokumentasi biasa</a> — BMAD project context adalah konstitusi implementasi untuk AI agents, bukan dokumentasi biasa</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">getting-started (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">literature (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"seeds":{"dendron.templates":{}},"enableFullHierarchyNoteTitle":false},"preview":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTags":false,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableK